    <abstract id="aspace_9d9a7af31ddc13056440a6358daa2f21">The collection consists of three reels of microfilm containing the family, baptismal, marriage, and burial records of the Church of The Ascension, a parish of the Episcopal Diocese of Pittsburgh located in Shadyside at 4729 Ellsworth Avenue.</abstract>
